.Sh NAME
.Nm AG_Menu
.Nd agar menu widget
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Bd -literal
#include <agar/core.h>
#include <agar/gui.h>
.Ed
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
widget implements a hierarchical menu system which supports text-based menu
and toolbar displays.
Individual menu items can bind to boolean values and specific bits in integer
values.
.Sh INHERITANCE HIERARCHY
.Xr AG_Object 3 ->
.Xr AG_Widget 3 ->
.Nm .
